data.description: Welcome to your updated haven in York, Nebraska! This home boasts recent upgrades including siding, windows, roof, gutters, soffit/facia, sewer line, and water heater - all completed within the last 2 years. Relax on the expansive front porch or entertain on the deck and patio out back. Inside, enjoy a remodeled interior featuring newer flooring, paint, kitchen, baths, and appliances. The main floor offers living, dining, kitchen, full bath, and mudroom, while upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms, a 3/4 bath, and laundry. With ample off-street parking and a basement for storage, this home is ready for the next owner!
